# Supabase SESSION POOLER (IPv4) — region eu-west-1, user postgres.<project-ref>.
# The Direct connection (db.<ref>.supabase.co) is IPv6-only and won't resolve on
# IPv4 networks, so we use the pooler. SSL is required automatically.
